displayProperties.name: Northerly Chill
displayProperties.description: In any Crucible activity, defeat Guardians with Stasis abilities. Earn bonus progress for defeating Guardians that have been slowed or Encased.

displayProperties.name: Void Ability Kills
displayProperties.description: In any Crucible activity, defeat Guardians with Void abilities. Earn bonus progress for defeating enemies with Volatile, Weaken, or Suppression.

displayProperties.name: Melee Ascension
displayProperties.description: In Crucible, Gambit, or Vanguard playlists, defeat any target with melee final blows in a single life. Earn bonus progress by defeating opposing Guardians.

displayProperties.name: Grenade Ascension
displayProperties.description: In Crucible, Gambit, or Vanguard playlists, defeat any target with final blows from grenade abilities in a single life. Earn bonus progress by defeating opposing Guardians.

displayProperties.name: Grenade Declination
displayProperties.description: In Crucible, Gambit, or Vanguard playlists, defeat any target with final blows from grenades. Earn bonus progress by defeating opposing Guardians.

displayProperties.name: Melee Declination
displayProperties.description: In Crucible, Gambit, or Vanguard playlists, defeat any target with melee final blows. Earn bonus progress by defeating opposing Guardians.

displayProperties.name: Solar Ability Kills
displayProperties.description: In any Crucible activity, defeat Guardians with Solar abilities. Earn bonus progress for defeating enemies with Detonate or Scorch.

displayProperties.name: Strand Ability Kills
displayProperties.description: In any Crucible activity, defeat Guardians with Stand abilities. Earn bonus progress for defeating enemies with Suspend, Infest, or Severed.

displayProperties.name: Big-Game Hunter
displayProperties.description: Eliminate a high-value target in Gambit.

displayProperties.name: Arc Ability Kills
displayProperties.description: In any Crucible activity, defeat Guardians with Arc abilities. Earn bonus progress for defeating enemies with Jolt or Blind.
